title: Dan Kennedy - The Ultimate Lead Generation Machine
description:
Every person knows that customers are the lifeline for every business but having a constant flow of leads is one of the biggest battles owners fight. Dan Kennedy, "The Millionaire Maker", has made it his mission to help business owners market better, make more sales and help more people. 

To stay inline with this, Kennedy and his team at GKIC have created a new program and an Ultimate Lead Generation Machine shows it maybe what many business owners have been looking for. The ability to generate as many leads as possible is the biggest asset that the most successful businesses have been able to achieve. With Dan's new program he has brought in experts who specialize in generating leads from various medium including postcards and direct mail, social media, SEO and various other online methods.
